{"attribution":"Occupational Safety and Health Administration, Electrical Safety, OSHA 4281-08 2023, Chinese Simplified; no OSHA or U.S. Department of Labor endorsement or affiliation is implied.","cases":[{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-electrical-safety-simplified-v1/sentence-001","input":"电会导致灼伤、电击甚至触电（死亡）等危险。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4281.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-001","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-electrical-safety-simplified-v1/sentence-002","input":"所有架空电线都可能已通电且为致命电压。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4281.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-002","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-electrical-safety-simplified-v1/sentence-003","input":"永远不要认为电线是安全的，即使它是垂下的或看起来是绝缘的。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4281.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-003","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-electrical-safety-simplified-v1/sentence-004","input":"切勿接触掉落的架空电线，通知电力公司该掉落的电线。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4281.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-004","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-electrical-safety-simplified-v1/sentence-005","input":"在清理和其他活动期间，与架空电线保持至少 10英尺（3米）的距离。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4281.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-005","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-electrical-safety-simplified-v1/sentence-006","input":"如果您在高处工作或处理长物体，请在工作开始前核实该区域是否存在架空电线。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4281.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-006","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-electrical-safety-simplified-v1/sentence-007","input":"如果在您驾车时，架空电线掉落至您的车辆上，请留在车内并继续驶离电线；如果发动机熄火，请勿离开车辆。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4281.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-007","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-electrical-safety-simplified-v1/sentence-008","input":"警告其他人不要触摸该车辆或电线。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4281.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-008","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-electrical-safety-simplified-v1/sentence-009","input":"致电或请人致电当地电力公司和紧急服务中心。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4281.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-009","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-electrical-safety-simplified-v1/sentence-010","input":"站在水中时切勿操作电气设备。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4281.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-010","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-electrical-safety-simplified-v1/sentence-011","input":"除非有相关资质和授权，切勿修理插线板或电气设备。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4281.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-011","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-electrical-safety-simplified-v1/sentence-012","input":"在通电前，让有资质的电工检查曾经受潮的电气设备。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4281.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-012","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-electrical-safety-simplified-v1/sentence-013","input":"如果在潮湿的地方工作，检查电线和设备以确保它们状况良好且没有缺陷，并使用接地故障断路器(GFCI)。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4281.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-013","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-electrical-safety-simplified-v1/sentence-014","input":"在靠近通电的地方工作时，一定要谨慎小心。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4281.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-014","split":"document"}}],"converter_output_used":false,"dataset":"blind-v2","id":"osha-electrical-safety-simplified-v1","input_only":true,"license":"U.S. Public Domain","modification_notice":"Extracted complete Simplified Chinese sentences from the checksum-pinned OSHA PDF, excluded the English page, URLs, phone instructions, page furniture, images, logos, and third-party content, and added input-only provenance; no expected text or converter output was used.","purpose":"candidate_source_pilot","review_policy":"domain_and_risk_must_be_assigned_from_input_only","source_class":"public_domain","stats":{"by_split":{"document":14},"eligible_pending_review":14,"exclusions":{},"raw_cases":14},"upstream_revision":"OSHA 4281-08 2023, Electrical Safety, Chinese Simplified; retrieved PDF SHA-256: 073a474bfa93e92f2e8dbc4c4fd36688bee6a81b5e4005e1679bd538f33ec6a6","version":1}
